sentence: In early trading on Friday, shares of Procter & Gamble Company (PG) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 1.3%.
Year to date, Procter & Gamble Company registers a 13.8% gain.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Intel Corp (INTC), trading down 9.5%.
Intel Corp is showing a gain of 11.1% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Exxon Mobil Corp (XOM), trading down 2.3%, and UnitedHealth Group (UNH), trading up 1.3% on the day.
